7,0.04379815,-0.02221653,-0.02717049,0.07159579,0.22085574,0.03640007,0.02244836,-0.02041927,-0.00424541,0.02216475,0.11897413,0.01863749,-0.0144841,-0.01549056,0.08015022,-0.01413004,0.02118306,0.03231799,-0.03510742,0.04289426,0.03805087,-0.04290592,0.04059119,-0.00176028,-0.08522908,0.02187226,0.09303934,0.04302697,-0.00058238,-0.04835933,-0.01652026,0.04355469,-0.03668112,0.04092001,0.01771677,0.00203156,0.00896055,0.0377862,-0.02001681,-0.02006259,-0.00836725,-0.02455945,-0.0059615,-0.01239803,0.02662703,0.10193393,0.0359519],"last_embed":{"hash":"1hlw2yh","tokens":510}}},"text":null,"length":0,"last_read":{"hash":"1hlw2yh","at":1769676455459},"key":"RemNoteExport_xdf--math_md_2026-01-29_04-43/pin/xdf 讲义/25高三\u0001寒假行远.md##{8}","lines":[403,648],"size":13982,"outlinks":[{"title":"图像变换","target":"../../图像变换.md","line":2},{"title":"分式函数","target":"../../分式函数.md","line":34},{"title":"中心对称","target":"../../中心对称.md","line":39},{"title":"三角函数","target":"../../三角函数.md","line":45},{"title":"图像判断","target":"../../图像判断.md","line":55},{"title":"零点问题","target":"../../零点.md","line":117},{"title":"0,1) \\\\ 1-|x-3|, x \\in[1,+\\infty)\\end{array}\\right.$, 则关于 $x$ 的函数 $F(x)=f(x)-a(0<a<1)$ 的所有零点之和为 $\\qquad$ （结果用 $a$ 表示）。\n                - \n            - 练 9-2\n                - \n                - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}e^{(x+1)^{2}}, x \\leqslant 0 \\\\ x+\\frac{4}{x}-3, x>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 函数 $y=f(x)-a$ 有四个不同零点, 从小到大依次为 $x_{1}, x_{2}$, $x_{3}, x_{4}$ ，则 $x_{1} x_{2}+x_{3} x_{4}$ 的取值范围为 $\\qquad$ .\n                - \n            - 例 10\n                - \n                - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left|\\log _{a}\\right| 1-x| |(a>0, a \\neq 1)$, 若 $x_{1}<x_{2}<x_{3}<x_{4}$,\n                - 且 $f\\left(x_{1}\\right)=f\\left(x_{2}\\right)=f\\left(x_{3}\\right)=f\\left(x_{4}\\right)$, 则 $\\frac{1}{x_{1}}+\\frac{1}{x_{2}}+\\frac{1}{x_{3}}+\\frac{1}{x_{4}}=$ $\\qquad$ .\n                - \n            - 练 10-1\n                - \n                - 已知函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}\\left|\\log _{4} x\\right|, 0<x<4 \\\\ \\cos \\left(\\frac{\\pi x}{2}\\right), 4 \\leqslant x \\leqslant 8\\end{array}\\right.$, 若存在实数 $x_{1}, x_{2}, x_{3}, x_{4}$ 满足 $x_{1}<x_{2}<x_{3}<x_{4}$, 且 $f\\left(x_{1}\\right)=f\\left(x_{2}\\right)=f\\left(x_{3}\\right)=f\\left(x_{4}\\right)$, 则 $x_{1} x_{2} x_{3} x_{4}$ 的取值范围为 $\\qquad$ .\n                - \n            - 练 10-2\n                - \n                - 设函数 $f(x)=\\left\\{\\begin{array}{l}-x^{2}-2 x, x \\leqslant 0 \\\\ |\\ln x|, x>0\\end{array}\\right.$, 现有如下命题, (1)若方程 $f(x)=a$ 有四个不同的实根 $x_{1} 、 x_{2}$ 、 $x_{3} 、 x_{4}$, 则 $x_{1} \\cdot x_{2} \\cdot x_{3} \\cdot x_{4}$ 的取值范围是 $(0,1)$; (2)方程 $f^{2}(x)-\\left(a+\\frac{1}{a}\\right) f(x)+1=0$ 的不同实根的个数只能是 $1,2,3,8$. 下列判断正确的是（）\n                - A. (1)和(2)均为真命题\n                - B. (1)和(2)均为假命题\n                - C. (1)为真命题，(2)为假命题\n                - D. (1)为假命题，(2)为真命题\n            - \n    - [03函数的图像与零点问题","target":"25高三\u0001寒假行远/03函数的图像与零点问题.md","line":200},{"title":"绝对值函数","target":"../../绝对值函数.md","line":229},{"title":"分段函数","target":"../../分段函数.md","line":233},{"title":"绝对值讨论","target":"../../绝对值讨论.md","line":233}],"class_name":"SmartBlock","last_embed":{"hash":"1hlw2yh","at":1769676455459}},
